

Welcome to OpenMetrics



* Installation

  Server
    - checkout or download/extract the om-tools to a server of your choice
    - execute ./om-installer.sh from within a shell - it will ask for some information


  Client(s)
    - checkout https://github.com/mgrobelin/om-tools to a host of your choice, e.g. the OpenMetrics server itself
    - execute ./om-agent-installer.sh <clients hostname> <hostname of OpenMetrics server>
    - NOTE you need to have an SSH server running on the client and a valid login for »root« user
